{{Quote|You're better than I am. I have to concede. I can't play against you if you always beat me like this. Here, take this. My old Pazaak mentor Daoy gave them to me when i started playing. Maybe they'll do you more good than they gave me.|Jolan Aphett to Revan|<ref name="KOTOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>
|translated=1}}
'''Daoy''' was a [[Pazaak/Legends|pazaak]] player who also taught students&mdash;including [[Jolan Aphett]]&mdash;how to play. Aphett was given several pazaak cards by his mentor upon departing for the tournament circuit.<ref name="KOTOR" />

